Here's the folder for the data file used in the R script. It's a slightly modified version of a table found on the WSER's website
(https://www.wser.org/).

The modifications I made were:
- Fixing the dates so the format is consistent between all years
- Adding the number of runners and finishers for each edition
- Modified the names of the column to make them easier to handle
- Adding the time for first man AND first woman (scrapped from Wikipedia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Western_States_Endurance_Run)
